  <refbody>
    <section>
      <title/>
      <indexterm>Translation Memory<indexterm>displaying properties</indexterm></indexterm>
      <indexterm>Translation Memory<indexterm>properties</indexterm></indexterm>
      <p>The properties of a <keyword conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/> are: <parml>
          <plentry><pt>Memory Name</pt>
            <pd>The name of the <keyword conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/>.
            </pd></plentry>
          <plentry><pt>Full Memory Name</pt>
            <pd>The name of the <keyword conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/>
              including its location.</pd></plentry>
          <plentry><pt>Description</pt>
            <pd>The description of the <keyword conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"
              />.</pd></plentry>
          <plentry><pt>Source language</pt>
            <pd>The source of the <keyword conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/>, this
              means, the language of the terms (headwords).</pd></plentry>
          <plentry><pt>Drive</pt>
            <pd>The drive where the <keyword conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/>
              resides.</pd></plentry>
          <plentry><pt>Last update</pt>
            <pd>The date and time of the last update of the <keyword
                conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/>.</pd></plentry>
          <plentry><pt>Size of index file</pt>
            <pd>The total size of the <keyword conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/>,
              in bytes.</pd></plentry>
          <plentry><pt>Different Segments</pt>
            <pd>The total number of different segments stored in the <keyword
                conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/>, which have different
              translations, which are from different languages or which have different markup
              tables.</pd></plentry>
          <plentry><pt>Markup</pt>
            <pd>A list of all markup tables used by the segments of this <keyword
                conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/>.</pd></plentry>
          <plentry><pt>Documents</pt>
            <pd>A list of the documents for which segments are stored in this <keyword
                conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/>.</pd></plentry>
        </parml></p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Prerequisites</title>
      <p>The <keyword conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/> must exist.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Calling sequence</title>
      <p>Select: <ol>
          <li>A <keyword conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/> from the <q><keyword
                conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/> List</q> window.</li>
          <li><b>Properties Summaryâ€¦</b> from the <b>File</b> menu</li>
        </ol></p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Results</title>
      <p>A document in HTML format is displayed containing a summary of the <keyword
          conref="common-symbols.dita#common-symbols/xlmem"/> properties (see <xref
          href="#viewtmprop/tmprop1win"/>) is displayed. <fig id="tmprop1win" expanse="column">
          <title>Memory Properties document</title><image placement="break" href="eqfb7s7v.gif"
              ><alt>Figure shows Memory Properties document</alt></image></fig></p>
      <p>If you want to view more properties or change the properties of a Translation Memory, refer
        to <xref href="xlmprop.dita#xlmprop"/>.</p>
    </section>
  </refbody>
